snippet.title: Kalasta // Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/1779450/Kalasta/

Kalasta is a roguelite deckbuilder fish game with real time strategy mechanics. Play cards to spawn fish, feed them and defend your fish from waves of monsters!

Developed by 
Tofu Bear
